trans-unit.source: Each property of the <xref href="System.Drawing.SystemIcons"></xref> class is an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object for Windows system-wide icons.
This class cannot be inherited.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the default application icon (WIN32: IDI_APPLICATION).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the default application icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system asterisk icon (WIN32: IDI_ASTERISK).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system asterisk icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system error icon (WIN32: IDI_ERROR).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system error icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system exclamation icon (WIN32: IDI_EXCLAMATION).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system exclamation icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system hand icon (WIN32: IDI_HAND).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system hand icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system information icon (WIN32: IDI_INFORMATION).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system information icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system question icon (WIN32: IDI_QUESTION).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system question icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the shield icon.
The User Account Control (UAC) guidelines recommend the use of the shield icon next to or on any control whose default action is to require an elevation to administrator privileges.
For more information, see the "User Account Control" section of the "Windows Vista User Experience Guidelines" on MSDN.
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the shield icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system warning icon (WIN32: IDI_WARNING).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the system warning icon.
Gets an <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the Windows logo icon (WIN32: IDI_WINLOGO).
An <xref href="System.Drawing.Icon"></xref> object that contains the Windows logo icon.
